{"tid":175997,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"矮是原罪！日本妹：「寧願揀高但普通樣，都唔揀矮靚仔」","createTime":"2017-03-28T01:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T02:55:03.000Z","uid":73064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96b13f49dff77a0a285237e5fe4e55bc460ef57c","tid":175997,"uid":73064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iR8qf98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiR8qf98.jpg&h=3b29c134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坊間一句「你的樣子如何，你的日子也必如何」，或許引證了不少社會現況，不過日本女大學生似乎另有想法。當要在矮小卻帥氣、以及高大但樣子普通的男生中揀出男友時，大多數日女寧願選擇後者。<br />\n<br />\n有網站訪問了286位女大學生，要她們選擇與「矮小型男」還是「高但樣普通」的男生拍拖，結果有75.2%女生表示會選擇「高男」，顯示樣貌無法取代身高的優勢。<br />\n<br />\n選擇高男的女生都表示：「我有個樣貌普通的男友就夠了」、「長得高好看一點」、「美男子已經夠多了」。<br />\n<br />\n而選擇另一方的女生，卻並非單單受帥氣樣貌吸引，她們稱：「我本身很矮所以沒所謂」、「因為我個子不高，要與高佬邊走邊說話很辛苦」等等。<br />\n<br />\n矮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56463786&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56463786%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170323&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=10b32d66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56463786%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170323&h=9692de7c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56463786&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170323</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8c9f6c6e473acea18f2c628f59d855d01600fa","tid":175997,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:26:17.000Z